items.title: Stock Market LIVE Updates: GIFT Nifty indicates a flat opening; US markets down, Asia mixed
items.description: Sensex Today | Stock Market LIVE Updates:  The S&P 500 and Nasdaq Composite ended little changed on Friday, overcoming a brief dip triggered by a Financial Times report indicating U.S. President Donald Trump was pushing for steep new tariffs on European Union products. The S&P 500 lost 0.57 points, or 0.01%, to 6,296.79, and the Nasdaq Composite gained 10.01 points, or 0.05%, to 20,895.66. The Dow Jones Industrial Average fell 142.30 points, or 0.32%, to 44,342.19.
